# Partner WebNLG saved models: keep only lightweight result files
partner/webnlg/saved_models/**
!partner/webnlg/saved_models/
!partner/webnlg/saved_models/**/
!partner/webnlg/saved_models/**/README.md
!partner/webnlg/saved_models/**/training_metrics.json
